I've understood "cycle 0" of a scanline to refer to the cycle during which the PPU outputs the signal corresponding to the pixel at x=0. This makes cycle 256 the first cycle of horizontal blanking.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Thu Jun 16, 2011 3:09 pm</p><hr />
